//Start Screen Of The Actual Interaction Start of the Interaction Now that you have decided upon the investments of the three products, you will be made to think in more detail about those decisions. This is done by presenting several questions. Your task is to read those questions and answer them for yourself. After you have done so, you should enter a number between 0 - 10 that indicates how confident you are in that you have considered the question well in relation to the company that you might invest in. After you have done that, you can make an investment based on new insights that might have arisen while thinking over the question.
